<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>스컬트 & 소울 - 프리미엄 필라테스</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            charcoal: '#2c2c2c',
            sand: '#e8e6e1',
            gold: '#c5a059',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            serif: ['Cinzel', 'serif'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-charcoal text-sand font-sans font-light">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center px-8 py-6 mix-blend-difference text-sand">
    <div class="text-xl font-serif tracking-widest">SCULPT & SOUL</div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex gap-10 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
      <a href="#about" class="hover:text-gold transition">소개</a>
      <a href="#classes" class="hover:text-gold transition">클래스</a>
      <a href="#studio" class="hover:text-gold transition">스튜디오</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-gold transition">문의</a>
    </div>
    <button onclick="togglePilates()" class="border border-sand px-6 py-2 text-xs hover:bg-gold hover:border-gold hover:text-black transition uppercase">
      예약하기
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero with Parallax Feel -->
  <header class="h-screen relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518310383802-640c2de311b2?q=80&w=1920" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 grayscale">
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center space-y-8 px-4">
      <p class="text-gold text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase animate-fade-in-up">Body • Mind • Spirit</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif leading-tight animate-fade-in-up delay-100">
        균형 잡힌 삶을 위한 <br> <span class="italic text-gold">우아한 움직임</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-gray-300 leading-loose text-sm md:text-base animate-fade-in-up delay-200">
        몸의 중심을 단단하게, 마음은 유연하게.<br>
        스컬트 & 소울에서 진정한 나를 마주하세요.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-8 animate-fade-in-up delay-300">
         <a href="#classes" class="border-b border-gold pb-1 text-sm tracking-widest hover:text-gold transition uppercase">클래스 보기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- About Grid -->
  <section id="about" class="py-24 px-8 bg-sand text-charcoal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-8">Refine Your Form</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          필라테스는 단순한 운동이 아닙니다. 내 몸의 미세한 근육을 깨우고, 
          올바른 정렬을 찾아가는 과정입니다. 저희는 클래식 필라테스의 원칙을 고수하며, 
          현대적인 해부학 지식을 더해 가장 효과적인 시퀀스를 제공합니다.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          프라이빗 레슨부터 소그룹 기구 필라테스까지, 
          숙련된 강사진이 당신의 몸에 맞는 최적의 프로그램을 제안합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4 font-serif text-lg">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="text-gold text-3xl">05</span>
            <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">Years Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px bg-gray-300 h-12"></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="text-gold text-3xl">12</span>
            <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">Expert Instructors</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518609878373-06d740f60d8b?q=80&w=400" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-tl-[4rem]">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1575052814088-64478839de8c?q=80&w=400" class="w-full h-64 object-cover mt-12 rounded-br-[4rem]">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Classes Carousel -->
  <section id="classes" class="py-24 px-6 bg-charcoal">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-gold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase block mb-2">Our Programs</span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl">Curated Classes</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex overflow-x-auto gap-8 pb-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto snap-x no-scrollbar">
      <!-- Item 1 -->
      <div class="min-w-[300px] md:min-w-[350px] bg-white/5 p-8 border border-white/10 snap-center hover:border-gold transition cursor-pointer group" onclick="togglePilates()">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition">Reformer Basic</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">초급 • 50분</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          기구 필라테스 입문자를 위한 수업. 
          리포머의 스프링 저항을 이용해 코어 근육을 강화하고 자세를 교정합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-gold font-serif text-xl">₩35,000 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-sans">/ 1회 (그룹)</span></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Item 2 -->
      <div class="min-w-[300px] md:min-w-[350px] bg-white/5 p-8 border border-white/10 snap-center hover:border-gold transition cursor-pointer group" onclick="togglePilates()">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition">Private 1:1</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">전체 레벨 • 50분</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          오직 당신만을 위한 맞춤형 시퀀스. 
          체형 분석을 통한 개인별 솔루션과 집중적인 케어를 제공합니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-gold font-serif text-xl">₩88,000 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-sans">/ 1회</span></div>
      </div>
      <!-- Item 3 -->
      <div class="min-w-[300px] md:min-w-[350px] bg-white/5 p-8 border border-white/10 snap-center hover:border-gold transition cursor-pointer group" onclick="togglePilates()">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition">Cadillac Flow</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">중급 • 50분</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
          캐딜락을 활용한 다이내믹한 동작으로 
          유연성과 근력을 동시에 향상시키는 중급자 프로그램입니다.
        </p>
        <div class="text-gold font-serif text-xl">₩40,000 <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-sans">/ 1회 (소그룹)</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Reservation Modal -->
  <div id="pilates-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-charcoal/90 z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4 backdrop-blur-md">
    <div class="bg-sand text-charcoal w-full max-w-md p-10 relative shadow-2xl">
      <button onclick="togglePilates()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-2xl font-serif hover:text-gold">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-2">Reserve Your Spot</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">당신의 변화가 시작되는 곳</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-6" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('예약 상담 신청이 완료되었습니다.'); togglePilates();">
        <div class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2">
           <input type="text" placeholder="성함" class="w-full bg-transparent outline-none placeholder-gray-400 font-serif">
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2">
           <input type="tel" placeholder="연락처" class="w-full bg-transparent outline-none placeholder-gray-400 font-serif">
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-gray-300 pb-2">
           <select class="w-full bg-transparent outline-none text-gray-600 font-serif">
             <option>체험 레슨 신청 (₩30,000)</option>
             <option>1:1 프라이빗 상담</option>
             <option>그룹 레슨 문의</option>
           </select>
        </div>
        
        <button class="w-full bg-charcoal text-sand py-4 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-gold hover:text-white transition uppercase mt-4">
          상담 신청하기
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function togglePilates() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('pilates-modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
